{"tid":115731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵應該就今次事件獎勵有份協助既市民","createTime":"2017-02-10T18:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T00:22:19.000Z","uid":69865,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e488e2668fa4aa776e617610cdecbb4e7d04909","tid":115731,"uid":69865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:35:13.000Z","msg":"就今次事件而言 千幾人得十個人(都唔知有無）幫手滅火<br />\n講緊係用頸巾等等 嘗試整熄個火 亦有人用滅火器救熄車廂個火<br />\n淨係咁既行為都值得表揚啦 反而你啲staff走晒佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836282d3596e61cf330c2691a63f9304445c9537","tid":115731,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:38:51.000Z","msg":"Staff 舉牌fing走d火？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0a3e6f3fd74754725935bf750989a96df3c890","tid":115731,"uid":34482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:39:00.000Z","msg":"職員去大堂幫手疏導啲人流好過啦<br />\n<br />\n再講一次，月台都冇危險<br />\n<br />\n有危險嘅話點會咁多人逗留拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678d197127b82cef325c2249bd11d2b7a33c8375","tid":115731,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:41:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b64a50ef86b31938bf74eff3fe557b1d06c47559","tid":115731,"uid":34482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"大把人仲想落去月台搭車 / 食花生，呢啲一落去，職員就係疏忽職守，冇阻止人落去<br />\n<br />\n月台如果真係咁危險，其實啲人會走晒，咁危險嘅話，職員都冇咩做到"},{"pid":"cddba57151e79823fa25b240d2e7519f408d9ede","tid":115731,"uid":69865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Staff 舉牌fing走d火？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n至少熱心幫人個幾位係值得表揚囉 唔係全部企係到拍片 食花生 笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdb4ceb2fb881ed723f4afb2c866063b113077d","tid":115731,"uid":34482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Staff 舉牌fing走d火？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n至少熱心幫人個幾位係值得表揚囉 唔係全部企係到拍片 食花生 笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國都有好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2a9218d88b1b76c6399be535d36cb402ba84e6","tid":115731,"uid":69865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:52:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>職員去大堂幫手疏導啲人流好過啦<br />\n<br />\n再講一次，月台都冇危險<br />\n<br />\n有危險嘅話點會咁多人逗留拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n憑咩判斷無危險？點知咩事著火？你驚死就走 唔驚死就幫人 不過唔係想鬧交 純粹覺得要表揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fed0767f31ffc28368db45394940e9461fc9dce","tid":115731,"uid":69865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:59:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大把人仲想落去月台搭車 / 食花生，呢啲一落去，職員就係疏忽職守，冇阻止人落去<br />\n<br />\n月台如果真係咁危險，其實啲人會走晒，咁危險嘅話，職員都冇咩做到</blockquote><br />\n香港人根本就無危機意思 比著外國走晒啦 仲企係到拍片咩<br />\n但重點係講緊千幾個香港人先得十個幫自己人 會唔會係有啲恐怖"},{"pid":"4707f400a3d968f04d677c65725baf78eea2ef45","tid":115731,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T19:02:05.000Z","msg":"每個月抽一日比佢地2蚊搭車囉"},{"pid":"a5ea07f4880f941ac83f4c43d53d85a925172574","tid":115731,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T19:02:17.000Z","msg":"都唔明連登仔做乜對呢單野咁emotional<br />\n現場係有成千人<br />\n但成千人有幾多果刻真係清楚發生乜事<br />\n見到有煙可能當狗鐵壞咗而已<br />\n卡尾都唔知卡頭發生咩事啦<br />\n唔係話佢地啱，走去拍片八掛有乜出奇<br />\n加上冇可能成千人都幫手救火<br />\n<br />\n燒傷嘅人係慘<br />\n但個個悲天憫人又屌邊個唔識急救邊個唔識逃走<br />\n根本冇考慮真正現場嘅人係咩感受"},{"pid":"7827dd45b809776f6d8b83ce652fc6319499d407","tid":115731,"uid":69865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T19: